DataSource.RecordSource: select Def.DepartmentID,Def.Code as Def,PL.ProductionLineID,PL.Code as ProductionLine,ST.LocationID,Loc.Code as Location, ST.BinID,Bin.Code as Bin,I.ProductID, I.Code as PartNo,I.Revision as Model,I.Description as PartName,CAT.CategoryID, CAT.Code as Category,ST.OHQuantity as OnHandQty,ST.ActualQuantity as ActualQty,UM.Code as UM,SO.Code as Source, ISNULL((Case When (Select UnitCost from v_UnitOfActualCost WHERE ProductID=ST.ProductID AND DatePart(Year,FromDate)=(Select DatePart(Year,FromDate) from IV_StockTakingPeriod where StockTakingPeriodID=3 ) AND DatePart(Month,FromDate)=(Select DatePart(Month,FromDate) from IV_StockTakingPeriod where StockTakingPeriodID= 3 )) Is NOT NULL Then (Select UnitCost from v_UnitOfActualCost WHERE ProductID=ST.ProductID AND DatePart(Year,FromDate)=(Select DatePart(Year,FromDate) from IV_StockTakingPeriod where StockTakingPeriodID= 3 ) AND DatePart(Month,FromDate)=(Select DatePart(Month,FromDate) from IV_StockTakingPeriod where StockTakingPeriodID= 3 )) Else ISNULL((SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ST.ProductID),0) End),0) as Cost from IV_StockTakingDifferent AS ST INNER JOIN ITM_Product I ON I.ProductID=ST.ProductID INNER JOIN MST_Location Loc on Loc.LocationID=ST.LocationID INNER JOIN MST_Bin Bin on Bin.BinID=ST.BinID LEFT JOIN ITM_Category CAT on CAT.CategoryID=I.CategoryID LEFT JOIN PRO_ProductionLine PL on PL.LocationID=Loc.LocationID INNER JOIN MST_Department DEF ON DEF.DepartmentID=PL.DepartmentID INNER JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure UM ON UM.UnitOfMeasureID=I.StockUMID LEFT JOIN ITM_Source SO ON SO.SourceID=I.SourceID WHERE Def.DepartmentID IN (8) AND PL.ProductionLineID in (1) AND ST.LocationID in (27) AND ST.BinID in (1)

Field.Name: fldTitle
Field.Text: REPORT OF STOCK TALKING RESULT AS OF
